1.0, \"rank\": 3.5383154421138186e-29, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"newspaper clippings\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"his past achievements\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the headlines read 'Gymnast reaches perfection', with the article explaining how he'd been awarded a 10 for one of his routines as a 12-year-old and was believed to be the only competitor from the region to gain that mark.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the headlines\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"Gymnast\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"the article\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"his routines\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the only competitor\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"that mark\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: 'As a lad gymnastics was my life\\u2026it taught me the simple recipe if you work hard, you get a result.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lad gymnastics\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the simple recipe\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without my sport I would never be where I am today \\u2026 #gymnastics #workhard.'\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"#gymnastics #workhard\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born and raised in Easington in County Durham where his father ran a newsagent's shop, Matt began competing as a gymnast whilst at school.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\", \"score\": 0.9999777715585336, \"rank\": 2.2228931411988658e-05, \"text\": \"Easington\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Easington_District\"}, {\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\", \"score\": 0.9999999978126652, \"rank\": 2.090269293875323e-09, \"text\": \"County Durham\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Durham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"a newsagent's shop\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, aged 14, he was forced to give it up after being diagnosed with anaemia.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anaemia\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later studied drama and was then cast in Blue Peter, a role that saw him win two Baftas for Best Children's Presenter two years in a row and a Royal Television Society award.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.422095112444741e-25, \"text\": \"Blue Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blue_Peter\"}, {\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Television Society\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Television_Society\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drama\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"two Baftas\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"Best Children's Presenter\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later competed on Strictly Come Dancing in 2010.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Strictly Come Dancing\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the Olympics Matt spoke about his past experience after some questioned his expertise.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Matt\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"his past experience\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"his expertise\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It makes me laugh when people ask, \\\"Why is the guy from Countryfile commentating on gymnastics?\\\"\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Countryfile\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Countryfile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the guy\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yes, I love the eclectic mix of things that I do and have done,' he told TV Times.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 2001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TVTimes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.743776319372395e-39, \"text\": \"TV Times\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TVTimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TVTimes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eclectic mix\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt, who started gymnastics when he was five, once told the BBC the sport was 'kind of a natural fit'.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9976869261064175, \"rank\": 0.0023163554666554512, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Matt\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural fit\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I used to bounce around all over the place.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be climbing trees and grappling up anything.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trees\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just clicked with me.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something that I loved, and I did not have to think about whether or not I wanted to go,' he said.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It wasn't like my parents were pushing me into it.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, to be able to express myself through movement is something that I thought, \\\"I have found it, and I want to do it for the rest of my life\\\".'\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"movement\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with thinning or dull hair?\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thinning or dull hair\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the real issue starts at your scalp Mother's Day gifts for new mums and mums\\u2011to\\u2011be under \\u00a350 The oral\\u2011care gadget making waves thanks to its powerful clean Dunelm's new outdoor collection will get your garden spring-ready - from just \\u00a33 The exact blush Margot Robbie wore in Wuthering Heights and best budget alternatives However, he said that after his anaemia diagnosis he made the 'really tough decision' to stop the sport.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.801003209120792e-12, \"text\": \"Dunelm\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\"}, {\"begin\": 2844, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margot Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\